Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • topdown.GameObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bullet, Enemy, PlayerSupplies, UserPlayer, Wall

    public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class used to monitor and alter the properties of GameObjects.
